statements.sql: select `addons`.*, `order_addon`.`order_id` as `pivot_order_id`, `order_addon`.`addon_id` as `pivot_addon_id`, `order_addon`.`verified` as `pivot_verified`, `order_addon`.`count` as `pivot_count`, `order_addon`.`price` as `pivot_price`, `order_addon`.`description` as `pivot_description`, `order_addon`.`id` as `pivot_id`, `order_addon`.`account_id` as `pivot_account_id`, `order_addon`.`payment_method` as `pivot_payment_method`, `order_addon`.`created_at` as `pivot_created_at`, `order_addon`.`updated_at` as `pivot_updated_at` from `addons` inner join `order_addon` on `addons`.`id` = `order_addon`.`addon_id` where `order_addon`.`order_id` in (16)

select `permissions`.*, `model_has_permissions`.`model_id` as `pivot_model_id`, `model_has_permissions`.`permission_id` as `pivot_permission_id`, `model_has_permissions`.`model_type` as `pivot_model_type` from `permissions` inner join `model_has_permissions` on `permissions`.`id` = `model_has_permissions`.`permission_id` where `model_has_permissions`.`model_id` = 1 and `model_has_permissions`.`model_type` = 'App\Models\User'

select `roles`.*, `model_has_roles`.`model_id` as `pivot_model_id`, `model_has_roles`.`role_id` as `pivot_role_id`, `model_has_roles`.`model_type` as `pivot_model_type` from `roles` inner join `model_has_roles` on `roles`.`id` = `model_has_roles`.`role_id` where `model_has_roles`.`model_id` in (1) and `model_has_roles`.`model_type` = 'App\Models\User'
select * from `payments` where `payments`.`order_id` = 16 and `payments`.`order_id` is not null
select * from `payment_links` where `payment_links`.`order_id` = 16 and `payment_links`.`order_id` is not null
select * from `order_items` where `order_items`.`order_id` = 16 and `order_items`.`order_id` is not null
select * from `expenses` where `expenses`.`order_id` = 16 and `expenses`.`order_id` is not null
